{"tid":491921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果CEO：不應指責中國","createTime":"2017-12-07T04:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T03:18:02.000Z","uid":70985,"like":15,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e5aa429a1407c19828b3bdb5fb22fdb53793c195","tid":491921,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/TIM-COOK_nTQFX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FTIM-COOK_nTQFX_1200x0.png&h=996fc227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》網站以〈庫克：不應指責中國〉為題報道，蘋果行政總庫克（Tim Cook）周三在廣州表示，當你到一個國家、進入一個市場，就要遵守該國的法律法規。<span style=\"color: red;\">為該公司按照中國政府要求將數百種應用從其中國應用商店下線的舉動辯護</span>。<br />\n<br />\n庫克周三在廣州發表演說時稱，中國市場是蘋果公司除美國外的第二大最重要的市場，避免在中國成為局外人很重要。報道指因為一些參議員和人權組織批評庫克參加中國政府本周早些時候在烏鎮舉辦的世界互聯網大會，庫克因而作出反駁。<br />\n<br />\n他周三在廣州舉行的《財富》全球論壇（Fortune Global Forum）上表示，當你到一個國家、進入一個市場，就要遵守該國的法律法規。<br />\n<br />\n庫克表示，你的選擇是，你是參與其中，還是作為旁觀者大喊大叫應該如何如何。他還稱，他自己強烈認為，你來到這裡並加入其中、參與競爭，因為旁觀改變不了任何事情。<br />\n<br />\n包括阿里巴巴主席馬雲在內的很多中國和西方企業高層管理人員在這次由《財富》舉辦的為期三天的活動上發表演說，庫克是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Cceo-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259Cceo-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a5dab674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259Cceo-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&h=a7da21f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Cceo-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奶共Cook"},{"pid":"cef844e051945f18c8a0b3300f381a5e9994f6a4","tid":491921,"uid":49588,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"睇來要轉會啦！"},{"pid":"ce940da9342f810679dbe693f559ee27a3f38ac0","tid":491921,"uid":107023,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"根本係大陸佬先禁鐘意用apple野"},{"pid":"dc829d80f8052461a88a6a18b797545326951809","tid":491921,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係大陸佬先禁鐘意用apple野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炮打司令部?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955217816df5e7a70cb4a91381ebadb321dde653","tid":491921,"uid":59898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用蘋果=奶共狗"},{"pid":"962a18f2040ae6d6888ea38e0ceb5b2af2bf3896","tid":491921,"uid":38539,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"咁事實嚟中國做主意要入鄉隨俗<br />\n中國國民普遍對國家政策無表示<br />\n名不正則言不順 外人仲點出聲喎"},{"pid":"25c600a1d0caf84604415cfaa9de77b7ab788f67","tid":491921,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁事實嚟中國做主意要入鄉隨俗<br />\n中國國民普遍對國家政策無表示<br />\n名不正則言不順 外人仲點出聲喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ce0a3535bdb0993abf2f30d4d9ee75ad2cc1ee","tid":491921,"uid":85163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fc2eac2c5e1010d881ddf57e8f16d58a0e610d1","tid":491921,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"Google好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f099351d8cdb174ac3122c04162dfee6b286fa","tid":491921,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,